rComments: HES SO LOVELY. yes, he goes on tangents but usually meant to help provide clarification or more information. Would recommend attendance for a good mark BUT he will applaud the effort made in class and loves to get to know his students on a personal level. Provides great life advice and very knowledgable, but you need to put in the effort to learn.
